I  would imagine that by now almost all investors must have noticed that if Johnson Joseph mentions anything in interviews or news releases at all
column3: it signals they have usually already worked on it for months and are ready to close a deal (imminent).  That is why we hang on every word he says or mentions anything if a form 7 or news release. If he says they are going to expand in the UK
column5: Brazil .. it signals they already had extensive talks with many connections etc.   If it was another CEO .. it usually might mean nothing or many months or years away or never happens. FOR new investors you must listen carefully to every sentence that  he says. His last famous quote of great significance  "  We will be a company that will raise $100's of millions of dollars and have revenue in the $billions "   That is all you need to know.. he usually does things in a reasonable amount of time and he always delivers
